<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.251042>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Balkanodesmus biokovensis gen. n., sp. n., holoype male (1 – 5). 1: habitus, lateral view, 2: body segments VIII – X, dorsal view, 3: body segments VI – VIII, lateral view, 4: gonopods, lateral view, 5: gonopods, in situ. Paratype juvenile female. 6: body end, lateral view. Scale line: 1 mm (1 – 3), 0.2 mm (4 – 5) and 0.5 mm (6)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/251042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.251044>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 and 12. Balkanodesmus biokovensis gen. n., sp. n., allotype female. 11: dorsal view of gnathochilarium and hypopharinx, 12: labrum. Scale line: 0.3 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/251044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

